<audio controls>
  <source src="audio/xyz.mp3" type="audio/mpeg">
  <source src="audio/xyz.ogg" type="audio/ogg">
  <a href="audio/xyz.mp3">XYZ audio recording</a>
</audio>

some browsers use .ogg

which of the following sets or returns the volume of the audio/video -> volume
following attributes adds audio controls, like play, pause, and volume -> controls
which of the following sets or returns whether the audio/video should start playing as soon as it is loaded -> Autoplay
which of the following sets or returns whether the audio/video should start over again when finished -> loop
which of the following returns a MediaError object representing the error state of the audio/video -> error
which of the following returns a TextTrackList object representing the available text tracks -> textTracks

